-- =============================================================================
-- QUID COMPANY PAYROLL TERMINAL
-- CompanyPayroll
--
-- Private-sector payroll only.
--
-- Government/public workers are intentionally excluded:
--   soldiers, guards, archers, knights, barracks/tower workers,
--   researchers, university/library/education roles, etc.
--
-- Public wages remain managed by the FED/GovernmentPayroll console.
--
-- Private company wages:
--   Unskilled = 3 Q/day
--   Skilled   = 4 Q/day
--   Elite     = 5 Q/day
--
-- Wage growth:
--   GDP bonus is the main growth driver.
--   Inflation bonus is deliberately weak and only kicks in when price index > 1.
--
-- Companies may overdraft. The bank records negative balances for now.
-- =============================================================================

